* Iron Raptor growled and bit deeper towards Zenyak as she heard him plea for help from Striker, if he was coward enough to ask for help from a Maximal then he wasn't worth keeping around.
Her teeth were bloody with his mech fluid and her throat was coated on the inside with it, but the taste was something yet to be desired!
It was then that Iron Raptor suddenly heard Zenyak yell out for his jets to activate, her not being in the mood to lose her prey simply jabbed her front claws towards his middle to snag and keep him from flying away.
But as a precaution and an extra step to keep Zenyak from escaping she then snapped her head towards his shoulder-plate and aimed to sink her teeth into it, thus adding the full weight of her head to stop him from taking off.
If he was brave enough to throw a grenade at three bots then he was able to pay the price...in his own fluid!!*
